===
title: WhereBerries
tags: 
speaker: Caravan Master Odema
colorID: 0
position: 2102,48
---
They grow on a bush that's common 'round here. Kinda funny looking. You'll know it when you see it. Doubt you'd have to go far off the road to find one.

