===
title: WhatRuins
tags: 
speaker: Caravan Master Odema
colorID: 0
position: 2103,294
---
Nothing you won't see on half the hills of Eir Glanfath. Money to be made selling their knickknacks in Defiance Bay, if you don't mind getting stuck with Glanfathan arrows now and again. They didn't build 'em but I'll be the Effigy if they don't watch 'em like a mother bear.

[[WhatRuins2]]
===
title: WhatRuins2
tags: 
speaker: Caravan Master Odema
colorID: 0
position: 2391,293
---
<<set $replyUnlockedWhoRuins = true>>

Course all the ones 'round here been ransacked ten times over, got nothing left worth half a pand.

<em>He adds, with a wink,</em> So I hear.

