title: WhatWeather
tags: 
speaker: Caravan Master Odema
colorID: 0
position: 2142,1092
---
This time of year? Rain mostly... and wind. But there's a different kind of wind out here, time to time. Locals call it a bîawac. Born outta the ether - the spirit's path. Never seen it myself, never care to.

