title: HugeRocks
tags: 
speaker: Caravan Master Odema
colorID: 0
position: 2140,1373
---
<em>Odema frowns.</em> They don't got adra where you come from?

Well, it just grows up outta the ground like this. Goes deep, like tree roots. Some of it all the way to the heart of the world, you believe the stories.

[[HugeRocks2]]
===
title: HugeRocks2
tags: 
speaker: Caravan Master Odema
colorID: 0
position: 2403,1370
---
It's more like a shell than a proper rock. Easier to work, if you're a mason.

Got all kinds of strange properties. Seems to have some kind of life of its own. Dies if it gets dug up. Loses its luster. Folks think it probably grew at one point or another, but not these days.

[[HugeRocks3]]
===
title: HugeRocks3
tags: 
speaker: Caravan Master Odema
colorID: 0
position: 2671,1370
---
The soul butchers in Defiance Bay use it for different things. I've heard tell it can hold a man's soul, but I don't care to see it. Got enough to worry about without seeing something like that.

